---
// src/components/HowItWorks.astro
---
<section class="py-24 bg-brand-dark relative overflow-hidden">
  
  <!-- Brillo de fondo sutil para dar continuidad visual -->
  <div class="absolute top-1/2 left-0 -translate-y-1/2 w-[300px] h-[300px] bg-brand-accent/5 rounded-full blur-[120px] pointer-events-none"></div>

  <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-6 lg:px-8 relative z-10">
    
    <!-- Encabezado de la Sección -->
    <div class="text-center max-w-3xl mx-auto mb-16">
      <h2 class="text-3xl md:text-5xl font-extrabold tracking-tight mb-4">
        Conseguir tu 0km es <br class="sm:hidden"/> 
        <span class="text-transparent bg-clip-text bg-gradient-to-r from-white via-gray-100 to-gray-400">más fácil de lo que pensás.</span>
      </h2>
      <p class="text-gray-400 text-base md:text-lg font-light">
        Sin vueltas ni complicaciones. Nuestro proceso está diseñado para ser rápido, transparente y 100% seguro.
      </p>
    </div>

    <!-- Grilla de 3 Pasos -->
    <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-3 gap-8 md:gap-12">
      
      <!-- Paso 1 -->
      <div class="group relative bg-brand-navy/40 border border-white/5 rounded-2xl p-8 hover:bg-brand-navy/60 hover:border-brand-accent/20 transition-all duration-300 transform hover:-translate-y-1.5 shadow-lg">
        <!-- Número de paso gigante de fondo -->
        <span class="absolute top-4 right-6 text-7xl md:text-8xl font-black text-white/5 group-hover:text-brand-accent/10 transition-colors duration-300">01</span>
        
        <!-- Icono SVG -->
        <div class="w-12 h-12 rounded-xl bg-brand-accent/10 flex items-center justify-center text-brand-accent mb-6 group-hover:scale-110 transition-transform duration-300">
          <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" class="h-6 w-6" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2">
            <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M15 15l-2 5L9 9l11 4-5 2zm0 0l5 5M7.188 2.239l.777 2.897M5.136 7.965l-2.898-.777M13.95 4.05l-2.122 2.122m-5.657 5.656l-2.12 2.122" />
          </svg>
        </div>

        <h3 class="text-xl font-bold mb-3 group-hover:text-brand-accent transition-colors duration-300">Iniciá la simulación</h3>
        <p class="text-gray-400 text-sm leading-relaxed font-light">
          Hacé clic en cualquiera de nuestros botones de <strong>Simular</strong> para abrir de manera segura nuestro asistente de cotización.
        </p>
      </div>

      <!-- Paso 2 -->
      <div class="group relative bg-brand-navy/40 border border-white/5 rounded-2xl p-8 hover:bg-brand-navy/60 hover:border-brand-accent/20 transition-all duration-300 transform hover:-translate-y-1.5 shadow-lg">
        <!-- Número de paso gigante de fondo -->
        <span class="absolute top-4 right-6 text-7xl md:text-8xl font-black text-white/5 group-hover:text-brand-accent/10 transition-colors duration-300">02</span>
        
        <!-- Icono SVG -->
        <div class="w-12 h-12 rounded-xl bg-brand-accent/10 flex items-center justify-center text-brand-accent mb-6 group-hover:scale-110 transition-transform duration-300">
          <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" class="h-6 w-6" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2">
            <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M9 12h6m-6 4h6m2 5H7a2 2 0 01-2-2V5a2 2 0 012-2h5.586a1 1 0 01.707.293l5.414 5.414a1 1 0 01.293.707V19a2 2 0 01-2 2z" />
          </svg>
        </div>

        <h3 class="text-xl font-bold mb-3 group-hover:text-brand-accent transition-colors duration-300">Completá tus datos</h3>
        <p class="text-gray-400 text-sm leading-relaxed font-light">
          Ingresá tus datos de contacto básicos en menos de 1 minuto. No requerimos información financiera sensible para calificar.
        </p>
      </div>

      <!-- Paso 3 -->
      <div class="group relative bg-brand-navy/40 border border-white/5 rounded-2xl p-8 hover:bg-brand-navy/60 hover:border-brand-accent/20 transition-all duration-300 transform hover:-translate-y-1.5 shadow-lg">
        <!-- Número de paso gigante de fondo -->
        <span class="absolute top-4 right-6 text-7xl md:text-8xl font-black text-white/5 group-hover:text-brand-accent/10 transition-colors duration-300">03</span>
        
        <!-- Icono SVG -->
        <div class="w-12 h-12 rounded-xl bg-brand-accent/10 flex items-center justify-center text-brand-accent mb-6 group-hover:scale-110 transition-transform duration-300">
          <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" class="h-6 w-6" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2">
            <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M8 12h.01M12 12h.01M16 12h.01M21 12c0 4.418-4.03 8-9 8a9.863 9.863 0 01-4.255-.949L3 20l1.395-3.72C3.512 15.042 3 13.574 3 12c0-4.418 4.03-8 9-8s9 3.582 9 8z" />
          </svg>
        </div>

        <h3 class="text-xl font-bold mb-3 group-hover:text-brand-accent transition-colors duration-300">Recibí ofertas oficiales</h3>
        <p class="text-gray-400 text-sm leading-relaxed font-light">
          Un asesor oficial de la marca que elijas se contactará directamente contigo para ofrecerte los planes de financiación a tu medida.
        </p>
      </div>

    </div>

  </div>
</section>